::Reptilica/DevilDuer::

Reptilica spins around as Feline yelled and fell unconscious, holding to 
pistols ready for whoever shot her.

"Hey, relax," DevilDuer says, walking out of the bushes and uncloaking, "Its 
me."

Reptilica looks from DevilDuer to the unconscious form of Feline. "Why in the 
pit did you shoot her?"

DevilDuer shruggs. "We can take her back to base and reprogram her this way. 
She'd be more loyal."

Repilica sighs, taking out a tube of liquid.

"What's that?" DevilDuer asks, looking at the tube.

"Its a modified form of cybervenom. It'll keep her in stasis lock untill I 
administer the antidote," Reptilica says, kneeling near Feline and injecting 
the liquid into her neck.

"Let's go," Reptilica says, picking up Feline, standing up, and flying off 
toward the Alliance base. DevilDuer takes off running, trying to keep up.
